title: Document AI - TrainProcessorVersionMetadata
abstract:
# Document AI - TrainProcessorVersionMetadata
The metadata that represents a processor version being created.| JSON representation                                          |
|:------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| { "commonMetadata": { object (CommonOperationMetadata) }, "trainingDatasetValidation": { object (DatasetValidation) }, "testDatasetValidation": { object (DatasetValidation) } } || Fields     | Fields.1                   |
|:--------------------------|:-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| commonMetadata   | object (CommonOperationMetadata) The basic metadata of the long-running operation. |
| trainingDatasetValidation | object (DatasetValidation) The training dataset validation information.   |
| testDatasetValidation  | object (DatasetValidation) The test dataset validation information.    |
content:
## DatasetValidation
The dataset validation information. This includes any and all errors with documents and the dataset.| JSON representation                                    |
|:-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| { "documentErrorCount": integer, "datasetErrorCount": integer, "documentErrors": [ { object (Status) } ], "datasetErrors": [ { object (Status) } ] } || Fields    | Fields.1                                            |
|:-------------------|:-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| documentErrorCount | integer The total number of document errors.                                   |
| datasetErrorCount | integer The total number of dataset errors.                                   |
| documentErrors[] | object (Status) Error information pertaining to specific documents. A maximum of 10 document errors will be returned. Any document with errors will not be used throughout training. |
| datasetErrors[] | object (Status) Error information for the dataset as a whole. A maximum of 10 dataset errors will be returned. A single dataset error is terminal for training.      |
